      <title>前莫桑比克部长因与瑞士信贷有关的欺诈行为被判有罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ex-mozambique-minister-guilty-of-fraud-over-credit-suisse-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克前财政部长曼努埃尔·昌因涉嫌参与瑞士信贷集团 20 亿美元债券欺诈丑闻而被判有罪，该丑闻引发了该非洲国家的金融危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/ex-mozambique-minister-guilty-of-fraud-over-credit-suisse-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 20:03:27 GMT</pubDate>
